<h1 className={"openapi__heading"}>Returns a list of label values for a provided label name</h1>

<MethodEndpoint method={"get"} path={"/v1/metrics/prometheus/api/v1/label/{label_name}/values"}></MethodEndpoint>



Retrieves a list of all values associated with a specific label name, optionally filtered by time range and series selectors.
